output:
Adventurous fox in the night,      
Bravely seeking an opportune fight;  
Cautious and sly the trek did last,   
Daringly facing dangers vast;  
Eagerly hunting for the foe,     
Frightened from coming face to face though;  
Gladly hoping for a safe return,
Honorably wanting lessons to learn; 
Impatiently waiting for the dawn,  
Judging enemies quickly gone; 
Keenly making the best of the time,
Listening for even the faintest chime; 
Maestro of the dancing night,
Noble knight in the morning light.
